text: Nicklas Kulti and Mikael Tillström were the defending champions but did not compete that year. Karsten Braasch and Jens Knippschild won in the final 7-6(7-3), 4-6, 7-6(7-5) against Simon Aspelin and Andrew Kratzmann. ==Seeds== # Joshua Eagle / Andrew Florent (First Round) # Mariano Hood / Sebastián Prieto (First Round) # Simon Aspelin / Andrew Kratzmann (Final) # Karsten Braasch / Jens Knippschild (Champions) ==Draw== ==External links== * 2001 Telenordia Swedish Open Doubles Draw Men's Doubles Doubles
